Marlton obtains financing okay to buy DMS . Marlton Technologies Inc said Monday it has received a bank commitment to provide the required financing for its planned acquisition of privately - held DMS Store Fixtures . The company also said that it has signed a definitive agreement to buy DMS for $ 14 . 5 million cash and up to 2 . 25 million unregistered shares of Marlton common stock . The terms of the deal , said the company , are in accordance with the letter of intent announced June 26 . The acquisition is still subject to additional conditions including approval by Marlton ' s shareholders . DMS supplies custom made fixtures and displays to national retailers , department stores and consumer products manufacturers . In 1996 it had sales of approximately $ 30 million . 
